{
  "stem": "268.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there were potatoes in it, and some like barley maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a really thick soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I never saw that kind soup in the barracks where they were, you know, where they were distributing in these little bowls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they really had thick soup and different soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember the greatest thrill for me was to come, and it was in the darkness, and it was already lights out, because lights were only on for half-an-hour or an hour after work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no reading period.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just to wash up and go sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would wake up, and I'd say, Dad, I got a soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would sit up in the bed, and we would scrape up the soup and eat the soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, I was so happy I could share a soup with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That would have made my day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As if, you know, this would really help him or help me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was a morale booster.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that camp-- that lasted till probably about November or December.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they liquidated that camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And again, we assembled and segregated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were marched to another camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it's a camp-- we marched to a station, rather, and again into boxcars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And again, a day or so-- the best I remember, probably a day, maybe a day and a half, we landed in another camp close to Breslau called Dyhernfurth.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was spelled D-U-- umlaut-- H-R-E-M-F-U-- umlaut-- R-T-H.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Dyhernfurth.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was somewhere close to Breslau, to Vrotslav.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that camp was really tough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was without the commandant that my father knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was different people and different nationalities too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were Ukrainians, Russians, some Czechs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And again, we were put to work in a factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
